      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, reboil a full kettle</p><p>Chop your <strong>cherry tomatoes</strong> in half</p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>chopped garlic </strong>and<strong> halved cherry tomatoes</strong> to the pan and cook for 3-4 min further or until the sausage meat is cooked through (no pink meat!)</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1580805931018-x200.jpg",
