            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the sausage meat is cooked through, add the <strong>tomato</strong> <strong>stock</strong> to the pan with the <strong>wilted spinach</strong> and give everything a good mix up</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
