        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Stir through your <strong>soft cheese</strong> and <strong>half</strong> your <strong>grated Italian hard cheese</strong> (save the rest for garnish!) and cook for 1-2 min further or until everything is combined – this is your <strong>spicy sausage & tomato sauce</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
