    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>spicy sausage & tomato sauce</strong> over the <strong>cooked spaghetti</strong></p><p>Sprinkle over the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>grated Italian hard cheese</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
